cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.CE 

This paper deals with optimization tasks that incorporate human preference feedback, which is a common problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also presents a new approach to extend an existing model, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and statistical inference (cs.SI). Finally, the paper discusses the practical applications of the proposed method in engineering problems, which is related to computer engineering (cs.CE).
